snippet.title: Cartel Tycoon - San Rafaela DLC Teaser // WISHLIST NOW!
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2348770/Cartel_Tycoon__Map__San_Rafaela/

San Rafaela DLC brings a new map, new story campaign, new characters, and more to the world of Cartel Tycoon! 

Cartel Tycoon is a survival business sim inspired by the ‘80s and '90s narco trade. Expand and conquer, fight off rival cartels, and evade the authorities. Earn people's loyalty and strive to overcome the doomed fate of a power-hungry drug lord.

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/CartelTycoon

https://twitter.com/CartelTycoon
https://www.facebook.com/CartelTycoon/
https://www.instagram.com/carteltycoon/
